message: /* R */ Mike Repole - entrepreneur. Co-founded vitaminwater and smartwater and sold to The Coca-Cola Company in 2007. Invested in Pirate's Booty and sold to B&G Foods. Now founder and chairman of BODYARMOR sports drink, Kobe Bryant is the #3 shareholder in BODYARMOR. Repole is also prominent horse racing owner, has had 4 horses compete in Kentucky Derby. Owner of the well-known horse, Uncle Mo. <ref></ref>
